en und Übergängen innerhalb unseres Kategoriensystems.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aCronenberg. 4aGrotesker Körper. 4aKörper. 4aKörpermetapher. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aTechnologie. 4aTransgression. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aBody.  aMedia Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z97831103707440 cprintz978383761740540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839417409?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839417409423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839417409/original  a978-3-11-037074-4  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013